  "faqAccountTitle": "Account and Registration",
  "faqAccount1Q": "How do I create an account?",
  "faqAccount1A": "To create an account, download the SRRFRR app, enter your phone number, verify the OTP code sent by SMS, then complete your profile with your personal information.",
  "faqAccount2Q": "Can I use the same account as passenger and driver?",
  "faqAccount2A": "Yes! You can switch between passenger and driver modes in the app settings. To become a driver, you must submit an application with your documents.",
  "faqAccount3Q": "How do I change my phone number?",
  "faqAccount3A": "Go to Settings > Profile > Edit Phone Number. You will need to verify the new number with an OTP code.",
  
  "faqBookingTitle": "Booking Rides",
  "faqBooking1Q": "How do I book a ride?",
  "faqBooking1A": "On the home screen, enter your destination, choose the vehicle type, check the estimated price, then tap 'Confirm Request'. A driver will accept your request in a few moments.",
  "faqBooking2Q": "Can I cancel a ride?",
  "faqBooking2A": "Yes, you can cancel a ride before a driver accepts without fees. After acceptance, cancellation fees may apply.",
  "faqBooking3Q": "How does Ladies-only mode work?",
  "faqBooking3A": "Ladies-only mode allows female passengers to be matched only with female drivers. Enable this option in your profile settings.",
  
  "faqPaymentTitle": "Payment",
  "faqPayment1Q": "What payment methods are accepted?",
  "faqPayment1A": "We accept cash and credit card payments. You can choose your preferred payment method when booking.",
  "faqPayment2Q": "How do loyalty points work?",
  "faqPayment2A": "You earn points with each completed ride, when referring friends, and by using the app regularly. These points can be redeemed for discounts on your rides.",
  "faqPayment3Q": "Can I get a receipt for my ride?",
  "faqPayment3A": "Yes, all your receipts are available in the ride history. You can download them or receive them by email.",
  
  "faqSafetyTitle": "Safety",
  "faqSafety1Q": "How does SRRFRR ensure my safety?",
  "faqSafety1A": "All drivers are verified with their official documents. You can share your ride in real-time with loved ones and report any issues via the app.",
  "faqSafety2Q": "What should I do if there's a problem during a ride?",
  "faqSafety2A": "Use the 'Emergency' button in the app to immediately contact our security team. You can also call authorities directly if necessary.",
  "faqSafety3Q": "Is my personal data protected?",
  "faqSafety3A": "Yes, we use bank-level encryption to protect all your personal and financial data. We never share your information with third parties.",
  
  "faqDriverTitle": "Becoming a Driver",
  "faqDriver1Q": "What are the requirements to become a driver?",
  "faqDriver1A": "You must have a valid driver's license, ID card, a vehicle in good condition with valid registration, and be at least 21 years old.",
  "faqDriver2Q": "How long does driver account validation take?",
  "faqDriver2A": "Document verification usually takes 24 to 48 hours. You will receive a notification once your account is validated.",
  "faqDriver3Q": "How are my earnings calculated?",
  "faqDriver3A": "Your earnings are calculated based on distance traveled, trip time, and current demand. SRRFRR takes a 15% commission on each ride.",
  "faqDriver4Q": "When can I withdraw my earnings?",
  "faqDriver4A": "You can withdraw your earnings anytime via your driver wallet. Withdrawals are processed within 1 to 3 business days.",
  
  "faqTechTitle": "Technical Issues",
  "faqTech1Q": "The app can't find my location",
  "faqTech1A": "Check that you have enabled location services for the app in your phone settings. Also ensure you have an active internet connection.",
  "faqTech2Q": "I'm not receiving the OTP code",
  "faqTech2A": "Verify that you entered the correct phone number and have network coverage. If the problem persists, use the 'Resend code' option after 60 seconds.",
  "faqTech3Q": "The app closes unexpectedly",
  "faqTech3A": "Try updating the app to the latest version, restart your phone, and ensure you have enough storage space available.",
